lic</span>\n\n\n      <span class=\"text-fg-dim whitespace-nowrap\">Last sync at</span><span class=\"text-fg\">05-07-2026 11:05</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"h-px bg-line-faded pito-detail-hairline\"></div>\n\n      <div class=\"text-fg-dim mt-1\">Description</div>\n      <div class=\"pito-video-detail__description text-fg whitespace-pre-wrap\">PITO is a minimalist, stubbornly focused YouTube tool for people who run more than one channel and got tired of YouTube Studio letting them see exactly one at a time.\n\nNo dashboards with forty tabs. No settings labyrinth. One chatbox \u2014 you type what you want, it answers \u2014 and that&#39;s the entire app.\n\nBuilt for me first. Open-sourced because maybe it&#39;s built for you too.\n\n#pito #gmrdad82 #youtube #rubyonrails #contentcreator #selfhosted</div>\n\n      <div class=\"h-px bg-line-faded pito-detail-hairline\"></div>\n      <div class=\"text-fg-dim mt-1\">Tags</div>\n      <div class=\"pito-video-detail__tags text-fg whitespace-pre-wrap\">Catalin Ilinca, talking head, storytelling, personal vlog, video blog, story time, honest conversation, no fluff, real talk, life stories, engineering, software engineering, experienced engineer, seasoned engineer, engineering career, remote work, tech savvy, gaming, passionate gamer, retro gaming, parenting, father, dad life, kids, family life, over 40, men over 40, dog owner, spain, valencia, personal development</div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n", "html": true, "video_id": 28, "list_footer": "Add what you need (game, at-a-glance via `with`). Drop what you don't (detail via `without`).", "origin_verb": "show", "reply_handle": "sigma-6069", "reply_target": "video_detail"}